{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Behind each mirror was an inmate, a Jewish female in a uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had-- They had hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were pretty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You sat down in the chair, within 30 seconds they shaved all of my hair-- and in my case it wasn't necessary but they did it anyhow-- under the armpits, all your pubic hair, and they had a bucket of green slime next to them with a little short-handled mop.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Strange how some things you remember-- I mean, it took maybe one minute.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After she shaved me, she pulled out this mop and poured this green slime on my head, under my armpits, in the pubic area. 'Raus.' You got out of the chair and you went forward to the other end of the room.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somehow or other my mother and I got separated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, I was short, so I even had a more difficult time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they thought they had enough of us, I can't tell you how many, they proceeded to beat the people at the very back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They opened this humongous door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it was an overhead door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, these are just impressions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by beating the people in a back, because I remember the screaming and the crying, those people tried to get away from it, and they pushed us in forward.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there I went with a mob.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There wasn't even a place to truly fall down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were body to body.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lock the doors behind us, and people were crying, screaming, praying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was then but I remember them saying, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I did not understand the Jewish prayers, but I do remember those words.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I heard a tremendous hiss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And, of course, bedlam.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
